Package: mizerAgents
Title: AI Agent Support for Mizer
Date: 2026-05-23
Type: Package
Description: Provides tools for setting up AI coding agents (such as Claude
    Code, GitHub Copilot, Codex, or Gemini) to work effectively with the mizer
    R package for dynamic multi-species size-spectrum modelling. Bundles a
    curated mizer reference card and API documentation optimised for large
    language models, and installs them into any mizer project with a single
    function call.
Maintainer: Gustav Delius <gustav.delius@york.ac.uk>
